### Get random fact
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/facts/random

### Get fact by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/facts/fact-134

### Get all facts (with pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/facts?page=1&limit=10

### Get all facts (default parameters)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/facts

### Get fun fact statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/facts/stats

### Get top rated facts
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/facts/top-rated?limit=10

### Get bottom rated facts
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/facts/bottom-rated?limit=10

### Rate fact
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/facts/fact-1/rate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 1
}

### Rate fact (negative)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/facts/fact-1/rate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": -1
}

### Import facts (Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/facts/import
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "facts": [
    {
      "id": "test-fact-1",
      "text": "This is a test fact for API documentation.",
      "source": "Test Source",
      "source_url": "https://example.com"
    }
  ],
  "skipDuplicates": true
}

### Seed database
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/seed

### Get real-time fact info (testing)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/facts/real-time

### Generate real-time fact (streaming)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/facts/real-time
Content-Type: application/json

### News ingestion cron job (requires CRON_SECRET)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/cron/retrieve-news
Authorization: Bearer {{cronSecret}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Topics API
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/topics?limit=10
